        <baseMoodEffect>6</baseMoodEffect>
      </li>
      <li>
        <label>Hallucinating</label>
        <description>Oh my god... The ceiling has tits now... or is that the sky?</description>
        <baseMoodEffect>8</baseMoodEffect>
      </li>
      <li>
        <label>Hallucinating Serious</label>
        <description>Holy fuck! Everythings just dicks! There is dicks and boobs everywhere. Wait... am I a dick?</description>
        <baseMoodEffect>6</baseMoodEffect>
      </li>
      <li>
